* David DeFeis – lead vocals, keyboards, synth bass, piano 
* Edward Pursino – guitar 
* Josh Block – bass 
* Matt McKasty – drums 
Former members
* Jack Starr – guitar 
* Joe O&#x27;Reilly – bass 
* Joey Ayvazian – drums 
* Rob DeMartino – bass 
* Frank Gilchriest – drums 

