<doc id="1047441" wikidata="Q3286483" url="?curid=1047441" title="Manon des Sources">
<text>Manon des Sources may refer to:

* &quot;Manon des Sources&quot; (1952 film), a French film directed by Marcel Pagnol, or the novel he published in 1962
* &quot;Manon des Sources&quot; (1986 film), a French film directed by Claude Berri</text><links>
<link wikidata="Q3286479" start="35" end="76" title="Manon des Sources (1952 film)" label="&amp;quot;Manon des Sources&amp;quot; (1952 film)"/>
<link wikidata="Q236630" start="104" end="117" title="Marcel Pagnol" label="Marcel Pagnol"/>
